    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基警告乌克兰盟友不要向普京示弱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/zelenskiy-warns-ukraine-allies-against-showing-weakness-to-putin</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·泽连斯基开始对欧洲国家进行为期三天的访问，以争取对其结束战争计划的支持，他表示，西方盟友的任何软弱迹象都可能让普京更加大胆。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/zelenskiy-warns-ukraine-allies-against-showing-weakness-to-putin</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 18:29:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国的借贷计划为一度夭折的项目注入新活力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/uk-s-borrowing-plans-breath-new-life-into-once-dead-projects</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国内阁大臣们再次讨论重大基础设施项目，包括一些被上届政府放弃的项目，这再次表明财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯正准备调整该国的财政规则，以允许更多投资借贷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/uk-s-borrowing-plans-breath-new-life-into-once-dead-projects</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 18:09:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>刚果希望摆脱中国对其矿业的主导地位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/congo-wants-to-pivot-away-from-china-s-dominance-over-its-mining</link>
      <description><![CDATA[刚果民主共和国最高矿业官员表示，该国正在为其世界级的主要金属矿藏吸引新的投资者，希望实现矿业所有权多元化，目前矿业领域由中国主导。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/congo-wants-to-pivot-away-from-china-s-dominance-over-its-mining</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 17:36:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波士顿写字楼价值暴跌 居民面临 28% 的税收上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/boston-residents-face-28-tax-increase-as-office-values-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波士顿市长 Michelle Wu 表示，如果马萨诸塞州立法机构未能在下月底之前批准暂时提高商业税率的提案，波士顿房主的税单将增加 28%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/boston-residents-face-28-tax-increase-as-office-values-slump</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 17:20:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布朗大学拒绝学生的反以色列提案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/brown-university-board-rejects-students-anti-israel-proposal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[布朗大学董事会投票否决了学生团体提出的提议，该提议要求其 72 亿美元捐赠基金中排除与以色列相关的资产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/brown-university-board-rejects-students-anti-israel-proposal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 17:17:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>六百万佛罗里达人被敦促逃离米尔顿即将到来的狂暴</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/florida-residents-urged-to-evacuate-before-hurricane-milton-landfall</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于主要飓风将在几个小时后登陆，德桑蒂斯表示，目前城市正在为应对影响做准备，仍有时间撤离。]]></description>
